<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Document</title>
    <!--引入css核心文件  -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.css">
    <!-- 引入jQuery  -->
    <script src="/js/jquery-1.11.3.min.js"></script>
    <!-- 引入js核心文件 -->
    <script src="/js/bootstrap.js"></script>
    <style>
        body {padding-top: 50px; background: #eee;}
        .main {background: #fff;}
        .main .media-left img {width: 370px; height: 200px;}
        .main .media{margin: 20px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 20px;}
        .hot li {line-height: 28px;}
        .footer {background: #101010; color: #666; padding: 15px 0;}
        @media screen and (max-width : 768px) {
            .media-left,.media-body {display: block;}
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-default navbar-fixed-top navbar-inverse">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="navbar-header">
                <button class="navbar-toggle collapsed" data-target="#menu" data-toggle="collapse">
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                    <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                </button>
                <a href="/" class="navbar-brand">牛的博客</a>
            </div>
            <div id="menu" class="collapse navbar-collapse">
                <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
                    <li><a href="/">首页</a></li>
                    <% for (var i = 0; i < cats.length; i++) { %>
                    <li><a href="/list?cat=<%= cats[i].title %>"><%= cats[i].title %></a></li>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>
                <form action="" class="navbar-form navbar-right hidden-xs hidden-sm">
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="请输入关键字">
                        <div class="input-group-btn">
                            <button class="btn btn-primary">搜索</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div>
        <img src="/images/baner.jpg" class="img-responsive">
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-9 main">
                <ul class="media-list">
                    <% for (var i = 0; i < posts.length; i++) { %>
                    <li class="media">
                        <a href="/posts?id=<%= posts[i]._id %>" class="media-left">
                            <img src="<%= posts[i].cover %>" alt="">
                        </a>
                        <div class="media-body">
                            <div class="media-heading">
                                <h2><a href="/posts?id=<%= posts[i]._id %>"><%= posts[i].subject %></a></h2>
                            </div>
                            <p class="info">
                                <span><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></i>admin</span>
                                <span><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-time"></i><%= posts[i].time %></span>
                                <span><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-eye-open"></i><%= posts[i].count %>浏览</span>
                                <a href=""><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-comment"></i>评论一下</a>
                            </p>
                            <p class="summary"><%= posts[i].summary %></p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <ul class="pagination">
                        <li>
                            <% if (page == 1) {%>
                                <a href="javascript:;">«</a>
                            <% } else {%>
                                <a href="?page=<%= page -1 %>&count=<%=count%>">«</a>
                            <% }%>
                        </li>
                        <%for (var i = 0 ; i < size; i++) {%>
                        <li class="<%= page == i+1 ? "active" : "" %>"><a href="?page=<%= i+1 %>&count=<%= count %>"><%= i+1 %></a></li>
                        <% } %>
                        <li>
                            <% if (page == size) {%>
                                <a href="javascript:;">»</a>
                            <% } else {%>
                                <a href="?page=<%= +page +1 %>&count=<%=count%>">»</a>
                            <% }%>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-xs hidden-sm">
                <div class="panel panel-default hot">
                    <div class="panel-heading">热门文章</div>
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        <ul class="list-unstyled">
                            <% for (var i = 0; i < hot.length; i++) { %>
                            <li><span class="label <%= i < 3 ? 'label-danger' : 'label-default' %>"><%= +i+1 %></span> <a href="/posts?id=<%= hot[i]._id %>"><%= hot[i].subject %></a></li>
                            <% } %>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="footer text-center">
        <p>版权所有，保留一切权利！ 转载内容版权归作者及来源网站所有，原创内容转载请注明来源。</p>
        <p>Copyright © 2013-2020 andy, All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
